<db:section xml:id="details">
<db:title>Detailed Description</db:title>
<db:para>A <db:link xlink:href="qt3drender-qpolygonoffset.xml">QPolygonOffset</db:link> class adds an offset to the fragment depth value prior to depth test and depth write. The offset can be used to avoid z-fighting when rendering polygons with very close depth values such as decals.</db:para>
</db:section>
